Package poo.main_project

package poo.main_project
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AcceuilController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "Acceuil.fxml", it handles all user input and logic for the GUI of "Accueil" page
    AchatController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "Achat.fxml".

    It handles all user input and logic for the GUI of "Approvisionnement" page:
    Adds a bought quantity for existing products.
    Adds a bought quantity for a new product.
    Displays the list of made purchases.
    App
    JavaFX App The main class of application.

    The program starts from here and loads the first fxml scene of authentification
    Categorie
    Class of the object of type categorie
    Client
    Client Class : Defines the clients of the store
    Inherits from the Individu Class
    ClientController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "client.fxml"

    It handles all user input and logic for the GUI of "Client" page
    It displays the list of clients and allows to extend it
    Facture
    Facture Class: Defines a bill for both sell and supply operations
    Fournisseur
    Fournisseur class : Defines the suppliers of the store
    Inherits from the Individu Class
    FournisseurController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "fournisseur.fxml"

    It handles all user input and logic for the GUI of "Fournisseur" page
    It displays the list of suppliers and allows to extend it
    Individu
    Individu Class : generic type of an individual meant to be either a client or supplier
    InventaireController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "Inventaire.fxml"

    It handles all user input and logic for the GUI of "Inventaire" page
    It displays the list of products in the stock, with their state
    Includes fiters
    JournalController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "Journal.fxml"

    It handles all user input and logic for the GUI of "Journal" page
    It displays the list of all ins and outs of the stock in the form of bills
    Includes fiters
    PrimaryController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "primary.fxml"

    It's the authentification page's controller
    This class handles all user input and logic for the GUI of "Authentification" page
    Produit
    Produit Class : Defines the products in the stock
    Inherits from the Class "Categorie"
    SecondaryController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "secondary.fxml"

    It's the main page's controller It handles all user input and logic for the GUI of the main page
    Contains the main layout of the app including the menu
    Allows to switch between scenes
    VenteController
    FXML Controller class for the fxml file "Vente.fxml"

    It all user input and logic for the GUI of "Vente" page
    Sells a quantity of an existing product
    Displays the list of made sells
